{"type": "article", "id": 36122, "title": "有了这面互动灯墙，儿童病房也可以很活泼｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-12-27T23:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 36267, "name": "AÃRK Collective"}, {"id": 36268, "name": "TAIYOU & C."}, {"id": 36269, "name": "ENESS"}, {"id": 33116, "name": "Rong Design"}, {"id": 23747, "name": "一融设计"}, {"id": 36270, "name": "XD Design"}, {"id": 36271, "name": "小林幹也"}, {"id": 36272, "name": "Jada Fitch"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 189, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161227230858cvumOGfiD5FgEpqb.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Bobby Compact by XD Design</h3><p>出远门时，你会用什么方式保护自己的贵重物品？来自荷兰的 <a href=\"http://www.xd-design.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">XD Design</a> 设计公司此前曾推出过一款名叫 Bobby 的防盗背包，随后又带来了迭代版 Bobby Compact。它的表面由五种防切割面料构成，其中还包括 6 毫米厚的防冲撞海绵层；隐藏式的拉链和多个口袋在杜绝扒手的同时也没有牺牲用户取用物品的便利。此前这款背包曾在<a href=\"https://izhongchou.taobao.com/dreamdetail.htm?spm=a215p.1472805.0.0.eEHuYv&amp;id=10062480\" rel=\"nofollow\">淘宝众筹</a>上集资，如果你错过的话，现在还能通过 <a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/bobby-compact-the-best-anti-theft-backpack-fashion#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Indiegogo</a> 参与众筹，最低价为 60 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161227231039UxWqvh85mf0GEoBS.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.670000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612272310390av4ZB3YTteo9Dwq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.116250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161227231039Wqy91xCvTuAanQfF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.256250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161227231039iH2FSCMlagQpzvsc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.535000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>AÃRK Collective</h3><p>AÃRK Collective 是一个来自墨尔本的腕表品牌，走的是简约的设计风格。赋予了这些腕表吸睛能力的不仅是旗下的四位设计师对几何图形的灵活运用，也在于不同材质间恰到好处的搭配。最近品牌还推出了一系列可替换的腕带，允许顾客尝试一些有趣的颜色组合。值得一提的是，AÃRK Collective 提供的包装盒也相当精致，让人有一种想为盒子去拔草的冲动。你可以通过<a href=\"https://aarkcollective.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>购买到这些腕表，售价为 189 澳元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161227231121IWRlTzftYLXBFy67.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.781481\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161227231121GZeWJb7DAx01Rv9s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161227231121jCRwGtsTYONMx8P5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161227231121CFPbH0ptATx7lGiZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.927344\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161227231121WOfShn4TgcIJ3815.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161227231121XNrZVHzoeLYUWylb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>TAIYOU &amp; C.</h3><p>日本设计师<a href=\"http://www.mikiyakobayashi.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">小林幹也</a>在 2012 年创立自己的工作室之前就对木制家具抱有浓厚兴趣，并且相当看好这一市场。今年，他成功创立了一个名为 <a href=\"http://www.taiyouandc.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">TAIYOU&amp;C.</a> 的家具品牌，并邀请到荷兰设计师 <a href=\"http://www.richardhutten.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Richard Hutten</a> 和日本设计师<a href=\"http://www.jinkuramoto.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">倉本仁</a>和自己合作设计了旗下的第一个系列，其中包括三把椅子和一张桌子。它们的造型都非常简洁，能够很好地融入周围的环境当中，体现出木料自然温暖的特质。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161227231208cKjXtxPpo3Vf0aFw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161227231206vyH5r9nSKZNmJI1o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612272312087GLjn2BRNvaDo6m9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161227231208TRYSG0kAMh5JnPZC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161227231206pdtvwXQmMGY0e47V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>LUMIS by ENESS</h3><p>在技术的帮助下，医院的儿童病房区可以在不需要全部重新改造的情况下变得活泼有趣。澳洲非营利医疗机构 <a href=\"http://www.cabrini.com.au/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Cabrini</a> 旗下的一家医院就在多媒体设计工作室 <a href=\"http://eness.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">ENESS</a> 和设计公司 <a href=\"http://www.designinc.com.au/\" rel=\"nofollow\">DesignInc</a> 的帮助下，拥有了一面可以互动的墙壁。它其实是一个名叫 LUMIS 的系统，木板内嵌有感应式的灯光，在访客经过时会自动触发特效，平时则和普通的木板无异。LUMIS 共有 15 种互动主题，并且根据昼夜划分，比如到了晚上才会出现的猫头鹰就会让经过的小朋友们感到惊喜。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161227231245UGrF9A7KaoeWLRb4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161227231245jriKVwQxyURchNql.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.137500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161227231246gNoPGaljRDQ6bvsU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161227231245rASNB9uZcsYxLdDl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Chickadee Houses by Jada Fitch</h3><p>有不少艺术家尝试着为小动物们设计如同人类居所一般的房子，出现在瑞典街头的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/35857.html\">老鼠餐厅</a>就是一个典型的例子。今天要介绍的鸟屋则位于美国缅因州艺术家 <a href=\"http://www.jadafitch.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jada Fitch</a> 的后院，她将漂亮的小房子固定在玻璃窗外，方便自己随时观察鸟儿的可爱模样。鸟屋的内部装修是 Fitch 用水彩画打造的，同时还配备了地毯、扶手椅和扫把这样的迷你家具。不过，鉴于它们目前还是脆弱的纸质结构，Fitch 计划未来用更坚固且防水的材料建一座新的屋子，好让鸟儿们驻足更久。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161227231351YLIay5skfBAr94DE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161227231351ap1KLJUmCSxV2Qe4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161227231352trGFpujSJAoNWe8f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161227231351mshdaPHkB304JiAK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Bamboo Tea Set by Rong Design</h3><p>装茶叶的茶罐如果也能用来泡茶喝会是什么样？<a href=\"http://www.rong-design.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">一融设计</a>为一间度假酒店的专属礼品所设计的包装就是由以竹节为灵感打造的茶杯、茶罐以及像是竹叶的茶勺所构成的，强调了茶道和自然的融合。堆叠之后能够转变为一段白色的竹子，晕染加工的淡绿色竹叶则起到了画龙点睛的效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612272313111Q7R9I35cFeB0wZu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161227231311wHSTn1xDc35KMZFI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612272313124stie85E7xJL0bNS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161227231312GmMjXw8nBQfZarSE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>"}